When sifting through an overwhelming amount of business data, sometimes you know exactly what you’re looking for. Other times you don’t, but you recognize it when you see it. Salesforce CRM Analytics gives you a fast, fluid way to discover the compelling stories within your data and to create the right visuals to tell your story.

See what unexpected insights you can surface by interactively exploring and visualizing your data using CRM Analytics tools. Use tables to get a view of the data that is close to the underlying dataset. Visualize your data with charts to understand vast amounts of business data and communicate that understanding with coworkers, partners, and customers.

Build upon a visualization by cloning its containing lens to a new tab where you can continue exploring. Save your visualization as a lens or share it with colleagues by posting to Chatter, getting its unique URL, downloading a screenshot, or downloading filtered data.
